# Input

```scss
%toolbelt{
border:1px solid black;
}

.action-buttons{
  @extend
%toolbelt
!optional;
}

.alert{
  @extend
.message,.info;
  @extend
a:hover;
  @extend
.icon-#{$name};
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
%toolbelt {
	border: 1px solid black;
}

.action-buttons {
	@extend %toolbelt !optional;
}

.alert {
	@extend .message, .info;
	@extend a:hover;
	@extend .icon-#{$name};
}

```
